songs.title: That Girl
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
See that black man, say peace
Leave that black man, say peace
All I'm tryna say is in the streets
Keep the peace, man, I keep the peace

[Verse]
If I gotta pray God, would you?
Different color jewelry look like different flavor color popsicle, uh
Summertime, like Slim Jim, hot pickle
I'm hot nigga, uh
Potato chips is five nickels
Same for the sunflower seeds
Promotin' love, bro, power, peace
All green, like the Garden of Eve
Popping like a hot pot of grease
Overseas like I'm European
Hold my nuts like I gots to pee
Hold my waist like I got to peace
Gave her D, put her right to sleep
All my chains, they 'bout it 'bout it
Open up my mouth like doctor teeth (Uh)

[Instrumental]
